OL,3,CBath's Thermae Spa will reopen today
OL,4,Cfollowing lorry crash
OL,6,FBath's Thermae Spa is reopening on
OL,7,FFriday 6 December after a lorry
OL,8,Fcrashed into its entrance.
OL,10,FOn Wednesday 4 December a delivery
OL,11,Florry reversed into one of the columns
OL,12,Fat the entrance on Bath Street.
OL,14,FThe column, which is part of an 18th
OL,15,Fcentury Grade 2 listed building, was
OL,16,Fsignificantly damaged, and the
OL,17,Fdecision was made to close the spa for
OL,18,Fsafety reasons.
