OL,3,CBath's Thermae Spa will reopen today
OL,4,Cfollowing lorry crash
OL,6,FSpecialist structural surveyors,
OL,7,Fstructural support contractors, and
OL,8,Fdesign consultants, quickly drew up a
OL,9,Frepair plan.
OL,11,FThe specialist team worked throughout
OL,12,Fthe night to fix the problem. The
OL,13,Fsolution was complicated by the fact
OL,14,Fthat the structure sits on top of 18th
OL,15,Fcentury vaults, so further stabilising
OL,16,Fwork was required beneath street level
OL,17,Fto stabilise the column using a
OL,18,Fnetwork of steel props.
