OL,3,CBath's Thermae Spa will reopen today
OL,4,Cfollowing lorry crash
OL,6,FAll the work means the Thermae Spa
OL,7,Fwill be back open from 12pm on Friday
OL,8,F6 December.
OL,10,FAndrew Jordan, Vice President of YTL
OL,11,FHotels UK, which operates Thermae Bath
OL,12,FSpa, said: ''We apologise to all our
OL,13,Fcustomers who had planned to visit
OL,14,FThermae Bath Spa over the past couple
OL,15,Fof days and we are grateful for their
OL,16,Fpatience and understanding. We also
OL,17,Freally appreciate the kind messages
OL,18,Fand well wishes we have received.
