OL,6,F"We are also grateful to our sister
OL,7,Fcompany YTL Construction who were on
OL,8,Fthe scene almost immediately and
OL,9,Fcalled in specialist contractors to
OL,10,Fassist. Thanks to their expertise and
OL,11,Ffor working through the night we are
OL,12,Fnow in a position to be able to open
OL,13,Four doors in time for what we
OL,14,Fanticipate will be one of our busiest
OL,15,Fweekends of the year.''
OL,17,FMore work will be carried out over the
OL,18,Fcoming months to restore the column.
